---
import Page from '../layouts/Page.astro';
---

<Page title="about -- alexander campos" description="Alex Campos. 26. Virginia. Operations, software, and writing about what sits underneath both.">
  <article>
    <h1>About</h1>

    <p>
      I'm Alex - 26, Virginia. I ship AI that runs where mistakes get audited. Three products live, one taking payments. Six years in regulated finance taught me the part most builders skip: someone has to be accountable for what the system does. So I build that in from the first line - local-first, audit-trailed, answerable to the person it serves. Not a lab. Where it counts.
    </p>

    <p>
      The day job is card legal recoveries at Capital One - monitoring systems, risk analysis, compliance, vendor coordination. The rest of the time I write code. A <a href="https://reframed.works">resume platform</a> that's live with payments. An <a href="/projects/forgeframe">open-source memory system</a> for agents. And sometimes I <a href="/writing">write about</a> how all of it connects.
    </p>

    <h2>Elsewhere</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="https://github.com/notaprompt">GitHub</a> — open-source work</li>
      <li><a href="/writing">the writing</a> — memory, provenance, and identity modeling, grounded in the neuroscience of memory and philosophy of mind</li>
      <li><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/alexander-d-campos/">LinkedIn</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://substack.com/@alexinthefield">Substack</a> — writing</li>
      <li><a href="#" id="influences-hint">Influences</a> — bookshelf</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>
      <a href="mailto:alex@campos.works">alex@campos.works</a>
    </p>

    <h2>Who's seen me</h2>
    <p class="seen-intro">
      Every system that watches you builds a model of you. Most never show it to you. Here is mine - everyone who has crossed this site, where they were, and what the machine thinks about you, right now.
    </p>
    <div id="seen-map"></div>
    <div id="seen-reveal" class="seen-reveal">reading the field&hellip;</div>
    <p class="seen-foot">coarse by design - the map holds cities, never anyone else's address. yours it shows only to you.</p>

  </article>

  <style>
    .seen-intro { max-width: 60ch; }
    #seen-map {
      margin: 1.25rem 0 0.75rem;
      border: 1px solid var(--white-08, rgba(255,255,255,0.1));
      border-radius: 4px;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: #0b0b08;
    }
    .seen-reveal {
      font-family: var(--mono, ui-monospace, monospace);
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: var(--white-70, #d8d4c8);
      background: #0d0d0a;
      border: 1px solid var(--white-08, rgba(255,255,255,0.1));
      border-radius: 4px;
      padding: 14px 16px;
    }
    .seen-reveal p { margin: 0 0 0.35rem; }
    .seen-reveal p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
    .seen-reveal b { color: var(--gold-accent, #e0b957); font-weight: 500; }
    .seen-reveal .sr-note { color: var(--white-30, rgba(255,255,255,0.35)); font-style: italic; }
    .seen-foot {
      font-family: var(--mono, monospace);
      font-size: 0.66rem;
      color: var(--white-30, rgba(255,255,255,0.35));
      margin-top: 0.6rem;
    }
  </style>

  <script is:inline src="/islands/world-map.js"></script>

  <script is:inline>
    console.log(
      '%c same question, different shapes. ',
      'color: #E8DCC8; font-family: monospace; font-size: 11px;'
    );

    // Influences discovery — hint toward the bookshelf on the desk scene
    var hintLink = document.getElementById('influences-hint');
    if (hintLink) {
      hintLink.addEventListener('click', function(e) {
        e.preventDefault();
        var canvas = document.getElementById('desk-scene');
        if (canvas) {
          canvas.scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth', block: 'center' });
          // Pulse the tooltip to hint at the bookshelf
          var tip = document.getElementById('ds-tooltip');
          if (tip) {
            tip.textContent = 'bookshelf';
            tip.classList.add('visible');
            setTimeout(function() { tip.classList.remove('visible'); }, 2500);
          }
          // Trigger highlight if desk scene exposes it
          if (window.__highlightDeskObject) {
            window.__highlightDeskObject('books');
          }
        }
      });
    }
  </script>
</Page>
